{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>……</p> ","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:24:17","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":3009},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>生活与互联网的高度融合，需要很高的技术作为支撑</p><p>需要花足够多的时间去创作未来的骁之屋网站</p> ","floor":2,"pid":8743,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:25:21","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3009},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>为了有足够多的时间创作网站</p><p>意味着我可能要削减人际交往支出，削减对外界的探索和体验</p><br><p>但这又是不可以接受的。</p> ","floor":3,"pid":8744,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:26:46","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3009},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>在有赞工作时 我每天要拿出120%的精神才能做好工作。</p><p>所以不可避免，工作会占用我的太多时间。</p> ","floor":4,"pid":8745,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:27:47","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3009},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>最好的办法 就是想出两全其美的办法</p> ","floor":5,"pid":8746,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:29:12","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3009},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>为什么需要在有赞工作？</p><p>一. 为了接触更前沿的技术，提升自己的技术水平（为以后更强大和复杂的骁之屋做基础）</p><p>二. 为了接触到位于更高层次的人，扩展自己的见识和交友圈（间接为了更精彩的生活做打算）</p> ","floor":6,"pid":8747,"postTime":"2020-01-12 23:34:39","replyCount":1,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":3009,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"如何在满足这两个目的的同时空出大量的时间呢？ ","createTime":"2020-01-12 23:36:51","id":3620,"replyId":0,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":1,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":1,"totalPages":1}},{